Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:19.06,Title,,0,0,0,,New Year's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some, I want some!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how we can get the nice food, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fool around, come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:00:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The one is ready. Take it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.62,Poem,,0,0,0,,Don't take something that doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:38.34,Poem,,0,0,0,,Virtue is owning up your mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One for each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Peanuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me first! I was the first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.22,Poem,,0,0,0,,Growing napa cabbages, harvesting chives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:29.10,Poem,,0,0,0,,Watering the garden and growing vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.10,Poem,,0,0,0,,Simple and happy lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Me first, I was first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy new year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.06,Passby,,0,0,0,,Be careful on the road
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.06,Passby,,0,0,0,,-You can leave now\N -Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:02:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run too fast
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.84,Passby,,0,0,0,,Tanghulu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.40,Passby,,0,0,0,, Tanghulu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:14.90,Default - down,,0,0,0,,Come with me, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,, Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, that tiger looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rooster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bawcock,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we have so many people in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't prepare anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My students being here means they respect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would dinning manners matter at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dishes are offered on the altar in the first lunar month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Water caltrops
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Water chestnuts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Glutinous rice balls
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The self-grown napa cabbage can also be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the hard work throughout the year is worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha, this is happy-new-year soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.96,Poem,,0,0,0,,Just like Hui, who lives in a poor place, eating simple food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.96,Default - down,,0,0,0,,*Yan Hui: the favorite disciple of Confucius and one of the most revered figures of Confucianism.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.98,Poem,,0,0,0,,Other people can't stand such poor life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.62,Poem,,0,0,0,,but we can find joy and containment in such life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, there are fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:12.94,Poem,,0,0,0,,♪ Amid the boom of firecrackers a year has come to an end. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:20.54,Poem,,0,0,0,,♪ And the spring wind had wafted warm breath to the wine. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:28.90,Poem,,0,0,0,,♪ While the rising sun shines over each and every household, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:45.34,Poem,,0,0,0,,♪ People would put up new peachwood charm for the old. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:45.00,Title,,0,0,0,,The end
